We tested our ‚Äúexecution‚Äù, ‚Äúsecurity‚Äù, and ‚Äútransaction‚Äù component in another test. A ‚Äúbusiness‚Äù component implemented a
‚Äúsecurity and access‚Äù interface, a ‚Äútransactional‚Äù interface and an ‚Äúexecution‚Äù interface. It was run on five processes. It first
checked the authority of the current user. Each of the process then updated a local copy of some shared data. We defined these
operations as a transaction.
